text_raw:
2. For the purposes of section 23(1)(b)(ii) of the Harbours Act 1996 (No. 
11 of 1996), the percentage to apply in respect of Dublin Port Company shall 
be 60 per cent. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
“Iris Oifigiúil” of 14th February, 2020. 

 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 I, PASCHAL DONOHOE, Minister for Finance consent to the making of the 
foregoing Order. 

[41] 3 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

6 February, 2020. 

PASCHAL DONOHOE, 

 Minister for Finance. 

I, PASCHAL DONOHOE, Minister for Public Expenditure and Reform 
consent to the making of the foregoing Order. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

6 February, 2020. 

PASCHAL DONOHOE, 

Minister for Public Expenditure and Reform. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

6 February, 2020. 

SHANE ROSS, 

Minister for Transport, Tourism and Sport.
